snippet.title: Bullets Squared Gameplay Teaser | FREE rhythm shooter on Steam
snippet.description:
Available for FREE on Steam: 
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1582960/Bullets_Squared/

Bullets Squared is a free, challenging minimalistic rhythm shooter, with colorful graphics, made up of 99% squares.

Follow me on Twitter for announcements, updates and rants: https://twitter.com/eNorby​

Designed and Developed by 
Norbert Érsek: https://twitter.com/eNorby​

Music by 
Andrew Sitkov: https://twitter.com/andrewsitkov​

Developed in Unity 2020.3
